formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The cost of land Rs. 13,22,33,800 has been taken for the purpose of this certificate. The acquisition cost has not been indexed for the purpose of this certificate.
2. The amount of on-site expenditure for development of entire project excluding cost of construction is taken as estimated by the management.
3. The amount of actual cost incurred and paid (Column -B) is Rs.47,50,66,656/- which exceeds the amount of estimates of (Column -A) Rs.45,29,52,818/- made at the time of registration. However the amount mentioned above in the cost incurred and paid column is limited to the extent of estimates, as in Gujrera Portal no option to increase the cost above estimation made at the time of registration.
4. The project has received the Building Usage (BU) permission from regulated authority, so any amount can be withdrawn by the management.
5. Dates mentioned in agreement to sale column in Annexure includes only dates of agreement and not lease deeds entered into with allottees as provided by the management.
